    AbstractState<T extends IPlayerData<T>>

    IPlayerData<T extends IPlayerData<T>>
    Represents the available game data of a single player.
    IPlayerState<T extends IPlayerData<T>>
    Represents the public knowledge and functionality of the game state.
    IRefereeState
    Total knowledge the Referee knows of the game state.
    PlayerState
    Represents the subset knowledge available for a player.
    PrivatePlayerData
    Represents the private game data of a single player.
    PublicPlayerData
